ESP8266 Power Sensor
====================

Counts pulses on an input pin and publishes current power consumption in Watt as well as daily total power consumption in Watthours to MQTT.

Uses https://github.com/avishorp/TM1637 which is not available via the platformio library manager.

How to use
----------
- Copy data/homie/config.json.template to data/homie/config.json
- Adjust values as required
- Compile with pio run, upload with pio run -t upload, upload config.json with pio run -t uploadfs
